      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Just want to add why usage of this operator indicates design flaws. The abstraction that needs to be cast to the concrete type doesn&#39;t provide enough information. It&#39;s either just some bad abstraction or abstraction that is used in a wrong domain. You can check detailed explanation with an example here: <a href=\"https://medium.com/@aerokhin/instanceof-should-be-your-last-resort-4b8b3667cd17\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">medium.com/@aerokhin/&hellip;</a> ."
